# Harness Ship — Automated Pipeline

You are running `/harness-ship`. **minimal-interaction** pipeline: run through and output the PR URL.

**Stop for:** on `{{ trunk_branch }}`; unresolvable rebase conflicts; in-branch test failures after triage; ASK findings; evaluation score stays below {{ pass_threshold }} after {{ max_iterations }} eval rounds.

**Do not stop for:** uncommitted changes; commit message or PR approval; AUTO-FIX findings.

