## Step 5.9: Eval Artifact Gate (mandatory)

```bash
harness gate --task TASK_ID
```

0 = proceed. 1 = fix (missing eval → Step 3.8; ITERATE → Step 5; stale → re-eval if needed). {% if review_gate == 'advisory' %}Advisory: ITERATE warning only unless eval missing/empty.{% else %}Eng: ITERATE blocks; only PASS continues. Score ≥ {{ pass_threshold }} enforced in Step 3.8.{% endif %}

---

## Step 5.95: Extract Failure Patterns

If this task had failures that were fixed, scan `code-eval-rN.md`/`build-rN.md`, deduplicate via `harness search-failures`, then `harness save-failure --task TASK_ID --phase <p> --category <c> --summary "..." --root-cause "..." --fix "..."`. Target 0–3 patterns. Zero failures → skip.

