## Step 9: PR landing

No `gh` → skip. Else loop ≤3: `harness pr-status --branch "$(git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD)" --json`; pass → success; conflict → rebase + `git push --force-with-lease`; fail → fix+push; pending → backoff (cap ~15m). **STOP** on infra-only, needs-human, exhausted, unresolvable. Success: update `workflow-state.json`, merge-ready summary, then `harness record-outcome --task TASK_ID`.

---

## Ship handoff

Write ≤2000 chars to `handoff_summary` in `workflow-state.json` (PR URL, commits, scores, findings, landing status).

