## Resume (short)

| Artifacts / phase | Resume at |
|-------------------|-----------|
| plan only, contracted | Step 1 fast |
| + build, building | Step 3 |
| eval ITERATE, evaluating | Step 5 |
| eval PASS, evaluating | Step 5.9 |
| gate PASS unpushed, shipping | Step 6 |
| pushed no PR | Step 8 |
| PR CI pending/fail, landing | Step 9 loop |
| PR green, landing | Step 9 done |

Do not re-run passed eval/tests unless code changed since.

---

## Important Rules

- **Never skip eval** (Step 3.8) or **gate** (Step 5.9). Tests alone are insufficient.
- **Never skip** ship review gate intensity rules; on dispatch failure degrade per **code-review-protocol.md**.
- **No force push** except `--force-with-lease` in Step 9 conflict recovery.
- **No trivial asks** — auto-commit/push/PR.
- **Bisectable commits**; **fresh verification** before push.
- **Goal:** `/harness-ship` → next output is PR URL.

Long-horizon loop SSOT: `feedback_ledger_path`, `continue_pause_summary` — see `/harness-vision`.
